WEBVTT

00:00.228 --> 00:01.516
<i>Previously on Banshee...</i>

00:01.541 --> 00:02.826
Who are you?

00:02.851 --> 00:03.944
I'm your grandfather.

00:03.969 --> 00:06.414
I bet you didn't know your mother
could handle a gun, did you?

00:06.439 --> 00:07.201
I'm gonna kill you.

00:07.226 --> 00:08.402
You already have.

00:08.427 --> 00:10.282
There's some men
they came here for me.

00:10.307 --> 00:12.019
- You want my help?
- I'll owe you one.

00:12.044 --> 00:14.441
Max, you don't have
to be scared of me.

00:14.466 --> 00:15.806
I would never hurt you.

00:15.831 --> 00:17.129
You'll always have a home here.

00:17.154 --> 00:18.352
- Thank you.
- Sure.

00:20.921 --> 00:22.002
Don't seem right

00:22.027 --> 00:24.300
burying the sheriff
with that pond scum.

00:24.387 --> 00:25.830
Your father and I
had a deal.

00:25.855 --> 00:27.016
We're not partners.

00:27.041 --> 00:29.342
You may cause me
to rethink my own terms.

00:29.668 --> 00:31.626
So you're a pretend
policeman now?

00:31.651 --> 00:34.880
I just wanted to be
the last face you ever saw.

