04:46.755 --> 04:48.123
<i>What do you want, Rabbit?</i>

04:48.157 --> 04:50.892
<i>I just wanted to</i>
<i>look into your eyes</i>

04:50.927 --> 04:52.828
<i>for the last time.</i>

04:52.863 --> 04:54.998
<i>Good-bye.</i>

05:06.509 --> 05:07.675
Oh, shit.

07:03.030 --> 07:05.132
I guess you owe me one.

07:38.733 --> 07:41.035
Hey.

07:41.069 --> 07:43.170
Go ahead.

07:43.205 --> 07:44.972
I don't want to play.

07:45.007 --> 07:48.273
But it will sharpen
your mind,

07:48.308 --> 07:50.404
teach you patience.

08:40.840 --> 08:43.440
<i>Holy...</i>

08:43.475 --> 08:45.175
shit.

08:46.377 --> 08:49.577
- Emmett, check the back.
- Jesus.

08:49.612 --> 08:53.512
Emmett, check the back.

08:54.780 --> 08:56.447
<i>- Hell.</i>
- We need an ambulance.

08:56.481 --> 09:00.384
<i>Hood, talk to us.</i>
<i>What happened here?</i>

09:02.187 --> 09:05.222
We just got here. Been out all night
looking for the kid.

09:05.256 --> 09:07.423
Nothing but dead bodies.

09:07.458 --> 09:10.326
Hood?
Sheriff Hood!

09:12.762 --> 09:15.363
I don't know what happened.

09:15.397 --> 09:17.231
They just started shooting.

09:17.265 --> 09:20.566
These are
military grade M4s.

09:20.601 --> 09:23.568
That's pretty high-end hardware for
this neck of the woods.

09:23.603 --> 09:25.770
All I care about now
is finding that boy.

09:25.804 --> 09:28.673
No, that's my priority
and that's my jurisdiction.

09:28.707 --> 09:29.983
In my estimation, Sheriff,

09:30.008 --> 09:32.428
you've become an impediment
to this investigation.

09:32.910 --> 09:34.778
I can make a phone call
to a judge

09:34.812 --> 09:37.547
and have a writ within the hour
suspending you from duty.

09:51.433 --> 09:55.369
Hood. Where the hell do you
think you're going?

10:02.010 --> 10:05.946
If you want to stop me,
you're gonna have to shoot me.

10:12.488 --> 10:14.258
Let me have your weapon.

10:28.606 --> 10:30.140
<i>What are you looking for?</i>

10:30.174 --> 10:32.475
I'll know it when I see it.

10:32.510 --> 10:34.510
I can help you.

10:34.545 --> 10:36.279
I've lived
my whole life here.

10:36.313 --> 10:39.181
Which explains why you haven't
grasped the concept of personal space.

10:39.216 --> 10:41.617
Just tell me what you got.

10:41.652 --> 10:45.187
<i>This is from the traffic camera</i>
<i>at the county line yesterday morning.</i>

10:45.222 --> 10:47.223
- How do you know that's him?
- New York plates.

10:47.257 --> 10:49.391
And Rabbit usually rolls
four cars deep.

10:49.425 --> 10:51.426
I tried calling our friendly
neighborhood sheriff

10:51.460 --> 10:54.295
<i>to put out an APB,</i>
<i>but he's apparently not taking calls.</i>

10:54.329 --> 10:56.427
<i>At least not mine.</i>

10:56.462 --> 10:58.061
I ran the plates,
they're counterfeit.

10:58.095 --> 11:00.026
But I ain't got no picture
of them leaving.

11:00.060 --> 11:02.127
- They're here.
- Think he's okay?

11:02.161 --> 11:04.662
<i>He's not okay.</i>

11:04.696 --> 11:07.330
<i>If Rabbit's here,</i>
<i>no one's okay.</i>

11:09.032 --> 11:11.200
<i>I told him, man.</i>
<i>I said over and over again</i>

11:11.234 --> 11:13.267
<i>we need to get the fuck</i>
<i>out of here.</i>

11:13.302 --> 11:15.968
<i>This has never been anything</i>
<i>but a terrible idea.</i>

11:16.003 --> 11:18.671
How do we find the boy?

11:18.705 --> 11:21.541
We hack into street cameras,
we look for the cars.

11:21.575 --> 11:23.643
We review security footage
from mini-marts

11:23.678 --> 11:25.912
and supermarkets--
someone had to do a food run.

11:25.947 --> 11:28.115
We reroute spy satellites
from the CIA

11:28.149 --> 11:31.085
and look for heat signatures
where they shouldn't be.

11:31.119 --> 11:35.456
This is a tiny needle
in a big motherfucking haystack.

11:35.490 --> 11:37.224
There's just too much
ground to cover.

11:37.259 --> 11:40.628
<i>I need 20 men doing this</i>
<i>and I ain't got 'em.</i>

11:40.662 --> 11:42.530
It's just us two.

11:53.256 --> 11:55.933
Or us three.

11:59.880 --> 12:02.118
Hey, Job.

12:02.152 --> 12:03.757
Long time.

12:06.500 --> 12:08.768
Gang's all here.

12:17.645 --> 12:19.613
Please.

12:19.648 --> 12:21.415
Keep trying.

12:50.658 --> 12:53.293
You know they're just here
to keep us safe.

12:55.129 --> 12:56.963
Hey.

12:56.998 --> 12:59.099
You okay?

13:09.477 --> 13:13.781
Deva, I'm sorry
about all this.

13:15.518 --> 13:18.086
Why would she
lie to us?

13:23.961 --> 13:27.230
Everything's not going
to be all right, is it?

13:30.969 --> 13:33.939
I don't know, honey.

13:34.006 --> 13:35.874
I honestly don't.

14:11.376 --> 14:13.508
I must admit

14:13.542 --> 14:17.043
you have an admirable
knack for survival.

14:19.813 --> 14:22.015
I'm already dead.

14:23.184 --> 14:25.718
- I know that.
- <i>Yes?</i>

14:26.920 --> 14:29.255
So why do you resist?

14:30.457 --> 14:33.126
You haven't offered
any other options.

14:33.160 --> 14:35.395
<i>Such as?</i>

14:39.300 --> 14:40.933
Surrender.

14:42.168 --> 14:45.137
You would sacrifice
yourself for the boy?

14:49.709 --> 14:51.576
No.

14:54.047 --> 14:55.883
For all of them.

14:56.920 --> 14:58.557
So...

14:58.591 --> 15:00.660
finally you admit

15:00.694 --> 15:03.230
your responsibility
in all of this.

15:06.735 --> 15:08.970
Yes, I do.

15:26.414 --> 15:28.315
<i>Uncle Kai?</i>

15:29.183 --> 15:32.018
- Hi.
- Hey.

15:33.554 --> 15:35.988
<i>I'm getting a glass</i>
<i>of wine downstairs.</i>

15:38.025 --> 15:41.427
I'm actually
gonna go to sleep.

15:41.461 --> 15:44.197
So good night.

15:45.633 --> 15:47.867
Good night, Rebecca.

16:35.276 --> 16:36.709
Ah!

16:54.125 --> 16:55.425
Who sent you?

16:58.095 --> 17:00.363
Fucking Indians.

17:47.803 --> 17:49.270
<i>Go help your uncle.</i>

18:07.722 --> 18:09.757
<i>You've been in a fight.</i>

18:09.791 --> 18:11.827
Just a misunderstanding.

18:11.861 --> 18:13.898
Do you want to tell me
about it?

18:13.932 --> 18:16.567
Someone had a crush on me,

18:16.601 --> 18:18.903
I just wanted to be friends.

18:37.256 --> 18:39.691
- Are we done?
- Not quite.

18:45.231 --> 18:47.998
Must be exhausting.

18:48.033 --> 18:49.801
What?

18:51.503 --> 18:53.737
Being on guard
24 hours a day.

18:53.771 --> 18:56.173
<i>Wondering where the next</i>
<i>attack is gonna come from.</i>

18:58.643 --> 19:01.145
Can you ever rest?

19:05.517 --> 19:08.319
I've been looking at
your initial police report.

19:10.389 --> 19:12.757
There were two of you
in that building.

19:14.660 --> 19:17.662
The police said that you had
made it as far as the woods

19:17.697 --> 19:20.237
where your chance of escape
would be much greater,

19:20.271 --> 19:22.710
<i>but yet you turned around.</i>
<i>Why?</i>

19:28.850 --> 19:30.985
Your accomplice...

19:33.455 --> 19:35.089
it was a woman.

19:39.027 --> 19:42.096
<i>These sessions are confidential</i>
<i>and inadmissible in court.</i>

19:42.130 --> 19:44.398
<i>You can't incriminate her.</i>

19:47.836 --> 19:50.338
You must have loved her
very much.

19:52.875 --> 19:55.610
<i>And you haven't seen</i>
<i>or heard from her since?</i>

20:01.883 --> 20:03.917
<i>I'm so sorry.</i>

21:01.642 --> 21:03.977
You okay?

21:04.012 --> 21:06.113
Yeah.

21:09.417 --> 21:11.918
So where you been?

21:11.953 --> 21:14.554
You know, around.

21:17.482 --> 21:19.714
Will you stay
for awhile

21:19.749 --> 21:22.080
now that he's gone?

21:25.648 --> 21:27.652
I could really use you.

21:29.156 --> 21:31.422
Well, that's not really
my bag, big brother.

22:02.891 --> 22:04.557
Ugh.

22:04.592 --> 22:06.424
Well, this is interesting.

22:06.459 --> 22:08.258
Oh, that motherfucker!

22:08.292 --> 22:10.425
<i>This is my home.</i>

22:10.459 --> 22:12.992
So you're upset
that the man

22:13.026 --> 22:15.359
who cut off the head
of the guy

22:15.393 --> 22:18.693
you sent to kill him
isn't respecting your privacy?

22:22.760 --> 22:24.192
What's this?

22:28.294 --> 22:30.427
It's one of ours.

22:36.094 --> 22:38.027
I'm thinking

22:38.061 --> 22:40.661
maybe I will stick around
for a while.

23:14.500 --> 23:16.899
This man will take
you home, Max.

23:28.267 --> 23:29.933
It's okay, Max.

23:32.101 --> 23:33.700
Hey.

23:36.068 --> 23:37.867
No one's gonna hurt you.

23:40.202 --> 23:42.235
Go.

23:56.206 --> 23:59.239
You trusted me
to keep my word?

24:01.808 --> 24:03.274
You always have.

24:13.613 --> 24:17.279
<i>Your call has been directed</i>
<i>to an automated voice mail--</i>

24:19.047 --> 24:21.514
- Still no answer.
- Keep trying.

24:39.953 --> 24:43.153
<i>It's okay.</i>

24:46.455 --> 24:48.255
Gordon.

24:48.290 --> 24:49.855
<i>Sugar.</i>

24:49.890 --> 24:52.122
What are you doing here?

24:55.524 --> 24:56.990
We got Max back.

24:57.024 --> 24:59.424
What? What do you mean?
How is he?

24:59.492 --> 25:02.458
He's safe.
He and Deva are with the FBI.

25:02.492 --> 25:04.225
He came home
a little while ago.

25:04.259 --> 25:06.492
- How?
- <i>He just rang the doorbell.</i>

25:06.527 --> 25:08.859
Said that they dropped
him off a block away from the house.

25:08.894 --> 25:12.127
I don't understand.

25:12.161 --> 25:14.595
What do you mean?
They just--

25:15.835 --> 25:18.372
they just dropped him off
just like that?

25:18.407 --> 25:20.842
No, not just like that.

25:22.278 --> 25:25.214
Your father told him
to tell you something.

25:25.248 --> 25:26.982
What?

25:28.451 --> 25:31.553
He said that you
were forgiven.

25:35.291 --> 25:38.692
- Hood.
- Max said they have him.

25:40.293 --> 25:42.259
He traded himself
for Max.

25:42.293 --> 25:44.928
I don't understand why Hood
would think that that's something--

25:44.962 --> 25:46.996
His cell phone.

25:49.133 --> 25:51.634
- What?
- I got a tracker on his cell phone.

25:51.669 --> 25:52.827
There you are.

25:52.852 --> 25:54.137
<i>What is that?</i>
<i>Where is that?</i>

25:54.138 --> 25:57.240
<i>The Bottoms near</i>
<i>the North Valley Woods.</i>

25:57.275 --> 25:59.542
What the fuck are the Bottoms?
What's out there?

25:59.577 --> 26:02.178
Well, nothing
that I can think of.

26:02.213 --> 26:04.448
Wait.

26:04.482 --> 26:07.584
The metalworks.

26:09.120 --> 26:10.921
We've been here all day
looking at these maps,

26:10.954 --> 26:12.988
moving satellites around
in outer fucking space,

26:13.023 --> 26:14.989
and then he says,
"Wait, wait, the metalworks."

26:15.024 --> 26:17.691
<i>Well, the Bottoms</i>
<i>aren't on most maps.</i>

26:17.726 --> 26:20.327
Is that it?
Is that it right there?

26:20.361 --> 26:21.895
Yeah.

26:27.034 --> 26:29.236
<i>What are you doing?</i>

26:29.270 --> 26:31.471
You call the FBI
and you let them handle this.

26:31.506 --> 26:33.173
- I can't.
- <i>You have to.</i>

26:33.207 --> 26:35.308
Now, I don't know what
Hood's role in all this is,

26:35.343 --> 26:37.266
<i>but we have two children</i>

26:37.291 --> 26:39.611
<i>whose lives have been</i>
<i>turned upside down.</i>

26:39.613 --> 26:43.649
Now, nothing and no one else
is more important than that.

26:49.690 --> 26:52.324
Come on, man.
Come on.

26:56.730 --> 26:59.198
Now, you lied to me.

26:59.232 --> 27:01.700
You lied to our kids.

27:01.734 --> 27:03.668
I don't know if you can
ever make that right,

27:03.703 --> 27:05.637
but if you're gonna try,

27:05.671 --> 27:08.473
you need to come home
with me right now.

27:08.507 --> 27:10.508
Gordon, don't do this.

27:12.845 --> 27:14.446
Don't make me choose.

27:14.480 --> 27:17.783
You go with them, you're
making that choice yourself.

27:23.790 --> 27:25.457
Um, what are you doing?

27:25.492 --> 27:28.394
Look, I've seen you drive.
Get in.

27:40.074 --> 27:42.342
We're probably gonna die.

27:44.578 --> 27:46.679
Probably.

27:49.016 --> 27:50.483
If we do die,

27:50.517 --> 27:53.252
I just want you to know
I don't like you very much.

27:58.458 --> 28:00.293
Duly noted.

28:00.327 --> 28:02.962
Well, if you're going
to drive, then drive.

28:02.996 --> 28:05.197
I want to be dead
or home by morning.

28:20.445 --> 28:21.980
Just drive.

28:29.489 --> 28:32.390
So your parole hearing
is in two weeks.

28:32.424 --> 28:34.292
Do you feel ready?

28:35.627 --> 28:38.663
Uh, yeah, yeah.
I think so.

28:38.697 --> 28:41.132
I know you're ready
to get out of here.

28:42.868 --> 28:44.836
You think
they'll let me out?

28:44.870 --> 28:47.472
You present as intelligent
and capable,

28:47.506 --> 28:49.641
as remorseful
and articulate.

28:49.676 --> 28:51.796
Plus, you have the single
best psych eval ever written

28:51.811 --> 28:53.979
in the history
of the prison system, so...

28:55.949 --> 28:58.250
Thank you.

28:58.285 --> 29:00.152
I just wish...

29:00.187 --> 29:02.288
What?

29:02.322 --> 29:04.123
Nothing.

29:04.157 --> 29:05.958
- <i>Come on, what?</i>
- Nothing, no. I'm sorry.

29:05.992 --> 29:08.060
- <i>I forgot myself for a moment.</i>
- It's our last session.

29:08.094 --> 29:10.328
You're never
gonna see me again.

29:13.365 --> 29:16.401
Um, I was gonna say
I just wish

29:16.435 --> 29:18.836
we had met under
different circumstances.

29:21.106 --> 29:23.574
I know it's
a pathetic cliché.

29:23.609 --> 29:26.745
No, no.
It's not.

29:28.315 --> 29:31.083
Um, you saved me in here.

29:32.719 --> 29:34.486
Are you scared?

